istrators     Help     Sandbox     Recent Changes                          in: Wizards, British individuals, Gudgeon family,     and 2 more    Males   Seekers             English     Deutsch   Polski               Galvin Gudgeon              View source                         History                         Talk (0)                                   Galvin Gudgeon   Biographical information  Born Before 1981[1]   Nationality British[2]   Title(s) Seeker[2]    Physical information  Species Human[2]   Gender Male[2]    Relationship information  Family members Gladys Gudgeon (possibly)Davey Gudgeon (possibly)Gudgeon family    Affiliation  Occupation Seeker for the Chudley Cannons[2]   Loyalty Gudgeon familyChudley Cannons[2]   [Source]  Galvin Gudgeon was a wizard who was the Seeker for the Chudley Cannons[2] Quidditch team in the 1990s. Whilst playing in a match against the Tutshill Tornados, Gudgeon fell off his Broomstick trying to catch a passing bumble-bee.[2]  Biography In 1998, he performed terribly when the Cannons were defeated by the Appleby Arrows. During the game, the Snitch bounced off his nose twice. Cannons manager Ragmar Dorkins felt he had to tell the team's fans that "turning him into a toad will not help his game."[2]  Appearances Daily Prophet Newsletters (First mentioned) Harry Potter: Wizards Unite (Mentioned only) Notes and references   ↑ As he was employed by the Chudley Cannons by 1998, he was presumably over 17.  ↑ 2.0 2.1 2.2 2.3 2.4 2.5 2.6 2.7 2.8 Daily Prophet Newsletters: 31 July, 1998, Page 2     Quidditch positions      Keeper   Raul Almeida · Ralph Heidelberger · Jonny Nuhaka · Lev Zograf · Denison Frisby · Bastien Janvier · Hermann Wiel · Barry Ryan · Tamotsu Iwamoto · Darren O'Hare · Martin Helstrom · Oliver Wood · Sendelina de la Felino · Merwyn Finwick  ·  Parkin · Grenouille · Kquewanda Bailey · Lenelle Paraison · Lachlan MacKenzie   Chaser   Alejandra Alonso · Fernando Diaz · Gonçalo Flores · Debbie Muntz · Gianni Fedele · Robert Green · Kenneth Hastings · Maria Monteith · Matthew Echunga · Unidentified Ballycastle Bats Chaser · Alexei Levski · Clara Ivanova · Vasily Dimitrov · Dragomir Gorgovitch · Avery Hawksworth · Edric Vosper · Keaton Flitney · Hildegarde Lafarge · Josephine Marat · Mathilde Mallard · Igor Brand · Kursten Blijk · Kurt Todt · Ginny Weasley · Wilda Griffiths · Moran · Mullet · Troy · Noriyuki Sato · Ryotaro Tanaka · Yoshihiro Suzuki · Alasdair Maddock · Fabius Watkins · Lorre Gustafson · Olaf Andersen · Peter Hansen · Ladislaw Zamojski · Catriona McCormack · Ana de Lebron · Carmen Garcia · Chavelle Arbelo Cartaya  ·  Joscelind Wadcock  ·  Petrova Porskoff  ·  Parkin (Chaser I)  ·  Parkin (Chaser II)  ·  Parkin (Chaser III)  ·  Gunhilda Kneen  ·  Radulf  ·  Otmar Frick  ·  Willi Wenzel  ·  Quentin Kowalski · Clairvius Hyppolite · Elodie Dembélé   Beater   Carlos Clodoaldo · Rafael Santos · Greg Ruczinski · Troy Duvall · Kelly Whakkaarangapawarau · Kylie Meadows · Finbar Quigley · Ivan Volkov · Pyotr Vulchanov · Joey Jenkins · Dawn Withey · Indira Choudry · Karl Broadmoor · Kevin Broadmoor · Alain Lacroix · Ninon Saucet · Elena Eldritch · Glockenspieler · Hesser · Katrina von Glockenspieler · Gwenog Jones · Connolly · Quigley · Minaka Hirakata · Keiko Takahashi · Asgard Pettersson · Asgeir Knutsen · Tiago Montoya · Dimitar Draganov · Vasco Santini ·  Parkin (Beater I) · Parkin (Beater II) · Ludo Bagman · Quintia Qarase · Narinder Singh · Ugga · Mercy Ojukwu · Aliko Okoye · Jean-Baptiste Bloncourt   Seeker   Tony Silva · Ariel Singleton · Maximus Brankovitch III · Gregory Cotton · Lucy Karoonda · Viktor Krum · Galvin Gudgeon · Blythe Parkin · Roderick Plumpton · Cybèle Peltier · Konrad Weiss · Josef Wronski · Glynnis Griffiths · Aidan Lynch · Shizuka Watanabe · Eunice Murray · Lennox Campbell · Tina Lundstrom · Benjy Williams · Dougal McBride · Inigo Fuente Marrero · Parkin · Joseph Snuka · Samuel Equiano · Bruno Bruunhart  · Jacques Miskine · Darius Smackhammer · Shanice 